title: Bam! Dutchess Shows Off New Man: Talks Leaving Ceaser Coming Up Off Black Ink [Video]
text:
Dutchess was in a new video with a guy dancing it up in the club, despite being in mid-season on Black Ink Crew . The tattoo artist took to social media discussing the video and being featured on the show without actually being in a relationship with Ceas.
Turn the page to see Dutchess respond to all the haters.
